snippet.title: Wavelength app launch teaser
snippet.description:
Download now for iOS and Android: https://www.wavelength.zone/play

Hot or cold. Soft or hard. Wizard or…not a wizard? Work together to decide where your clue falls on the spectrum – and win by reading your friends’ minds.

"It's one of the best party games we've played." – Apple Design Award Finalist & Editors' Choice 
“Absolutely phenomenal.” – SHUT UP & SIT DOWN
“One of the best party games we’ve ever played.” – POLYGON
“The best party game since Codenames.” – DICEBREAKER

Music: Upright T-Rex
